        <h2>Heartland Town Centre</h2>
        <p>
            Heartland Town Centre, one of Canada’s largest and most successful Power Centres offers over 163 stores and services for ultimate shopping experience. Currently 2 million square feet of space constructed boasting Canada’s most successful major tenant mix including: Best Buy, Canadian Tire, Constco, Future Shop, H&M, Home Depot, Home Outfitters, HomeSense, Loblaws, Michaels, Petsmart, Staples, Stylesense, The Brick, Wlamart and Winners. Heartland also provides a wide range of eating establishments including Baton Rouge, Casey’s, East Side Mario’s, Milestone, The Keg, Tucker’s Marketplace and numberous fast food providers such as A&W, McDonald’s, Made in Japan Teriyaki Expereince, Mr. Greek, Nando’s Chickenland and Second Cup.
